18269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賤男短期內都唔會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係一個好例子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇一絲內疚<br />\n唔會心疼你條女咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有內疚既<br />\n但係分左手幾個月之後 佢真係無搵我先咁<br />\n想搵d女溝下 但結果發覺投入唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好牽強既內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情場高手"},{"pid":"9b3b547cec3b4def3ea3598ca5f41343b2e3c7df","tid":283423,"uid":18269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免費雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b14e2d9433ccd7dbae1da79b855ec7f94337e4","tid":283423,"uid":40735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我女朋友都送帽我戴，佢要求分手<br />\n但分左手都仲係咁話愛我想見我，但又走去見條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然揀左就算9數啦，唔好再煩我啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點樣做到咁果斷<br />\n<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都拍左4年幾<br />\n其實我又唔係即刻咁果斷<br />\n一開始都有好唔捨得，想佢返黎我身邊<br />\n會有好多心軟既時候，諗住佢返黎就咩都算喇唔計喇<br />\n但佢都係揀左條友，話唔夾再返黎搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就算9數啦，我已經明白個心已經唔喺我度，我想搵個對我一樣咁專一既人<br />\n就算有一日佢後悔都不了，唔想成世提心吊膽，諗起佢可以咁背叛我，唔珍惜依段感情，第時難保唔會有第二個<br />\n長痛不如短痛"},{"pid":"fba53f0092037a3326c4e4e78a652029be15b5ba","tid":283423,"uid":68258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定唔撚係真愛囉<br />\n但明知對方仆街但又犯賤到想原諒真係好痛苦嘅感受